Command to create a directory:
 mkdir <directory-name>
 mkdir -v <directory-name>
 mkdir -m 777 <directory-name>
 mkdir -p <directory-name>/<directory-name>...

Command to delete a directory:
    -->Incase of empty directory
          rmdir <directory-name>
    -->Incase of non-empty directories
          rm <directory-name>
	  rm -r <directory-name>
	  rm -rf <directory-name>
